title: Annemarie Munk

sentences.sentence: Annemarie Munk (born 25 March 1974) is a Hong Kong swimmer
She competed in four events at the 1988 Summer Olympics
She was educated at Island School and Deerfield Academy, before enrolling at the University of Southern California
Munk is the cofounder of Swim Lab Asia, a triathlon and open water swimming coaching business, and as of 2018 was the director and head coach
Munk is also a board member and the director of programs for Splash Foundation, a charity swim school for the underprivileged and under-resourced community in Hong Kong
